  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 367ff6cdabe6d8f4ebb341c32007b399, type: 3}
  m_Name: DebugInfoSetup
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp-Editor::DebugInfoDescriptionSetup
  DebugInfo:
  - "Ending setup - pod GameManagerem mamy obiekt GameplayManager i na nim komponent
    GameState, a tam s\u0105 guziki\nOg\xF3lnie mo\u017Cna to przejrze\u0107, bo
    tam s\u0105 r\xF3\u017Cne guziki na obiektach pod GameManagerem"
  - "Na scriptable'ach quest\xF3w mo\u017Cna je zaczyna\u0107 i ko\u0144czy\u0107
    guzikiem"
  - Mamy okienko z custom gizmo na scene view
  - 'Bindingi:

    M - toggle monster interactions

    Shift - toggle sprint

    U
    - toggle time scale na 50

    N - toggle no clip '
  - 'Gizmosy:

    - trigger: player (pink), monster (yellow)

    - interactable:
    glitch (pink), pickable (yellow), simple dialogue (green), lock (red), disabled
    (transparent)'
  - "Unity Eventy:\n- Monster/Player trigger\n- Interactable\n- Drzwi/furtka\n- Burza\n-
    Unlockable\n- Monster State - pod obiektem mamy stany potwora i mo\u017Cna wpi\u0105\u0107
    rzeczy na OnEnter i OnExit do ka\u017Cdego stanu"
